rio-64">Super Mario 64</a></em> on the Nintendo 64! It brought back a lot of memories during these 110 km! I would never have thought that one day I would trace him in the streets of Paris [but] this time, it was him who played with me and not the other way around!”</p><p> The drawing was then shared on X by <a href="https://x.com/Nintendeal/status/1899192477673984286" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Nintendeal</a> , where it racked up more than 150,000 views. “Now that&#39;s real dedication, you have to respect a person like that,” <a href="https://x.com/TheLostKorok/status/1899206576046506259" target="_blank" rel="noopener">wrote</a> one impressed fan while another <a href="https://x.com/Krillbs/status/1899217402857947607" target="_blank" rel="noopener">joked</a> Lazert was about to get “sued” by Nintendo.</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> Whats the chances they get sued by Nintendo <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f480.png" alt="💀" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://t.co/c6mB8s6KOU">https://t.co/c6mB8s6KOU</a></p><p> — Krillbs (@Krillbs) <a href="https://twitter.com/Krillbs/status/1899217402857947607?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">March 10, 2025</a> </p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> The drawing was in celebration of Mario Day, an annual celebration of Nintendo&#39;s mascot.任天堂获得喜庆的心情，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/mario-game-annoucement-switch-2-pre-order-3844061">确认了经典马里奥冠军以及特别的<em>Mario Kart 8 Deluxe</em>锦标赛的折扣。</a> However, there were no new game announcements with Nintendo presumably saving those for its upcoming Switch 2 Direct presentation which is happening next month.</p><p> The new console was <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/nintendo-switch-2-release-date-price-games-3829607">officially confirmed earlier this year</a> with a brief hard